हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा।

show.description: Vedant, a hidden billionaire, sacrifices his identity for love—only to be betrayed by the very woman he trusted most. Fate binds him to powerful businesswoman Tara in a contract marriage, where love, revenge, and secrets collide. In this storm of emotions, emerges… The Ultimate Boss.
